{"id":2417,"date":"2019-11-19T16:32:17","date_gmt":"2019-11-19T09:32:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?post_type=product&#038;p=2417"},"modified":"2019-11-20T17:09:15","modified_gmt":"2019-11-20T10:09:15","slug":"rem-cua-nam-dinh-cho-phong-khach-biet-thu-sieu-dep","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-cua-nam-dinh-cho-phong-khach-biet-thu-sieu-dep","title":{"rendered":"R\u00e8m c\u1eeda Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 140%;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 mang phong c\u00e1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, n\u00ean Ch\u1ecb Th\u1ee7y t\u1ea1i Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng quen c\u1ee7a\u00a0<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\"> <a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\">R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<\/a> <\/span><\/span>\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1eafp \u0111\u0103t b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda cao c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m to\u00e1t l\u00ean v\u1ebb sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi thanh ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n cao c\u1ea5p t\u0129nh \u0111i\u1ec7n ch\u1ed1ng \u1ed3n v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u00e8m c\u1eeda t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u Ghi sang tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ec1n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb l\u1ed7i m\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Hi\u1ec7n nay<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\"> <a style=\"color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\">r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp <\/a><\/span>\u00a0<\/span>\u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft b\u1edfi hai l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i: 1 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i voan nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng b\u00ean trong v\u00e0 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i H\u00e0n cao c\u1ea5p b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea1o cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u1eeba nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1eeba \u1ea5m c\u00fang. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong l\u0129nh v\u1eeba r\u00e8m c\u1eeda cao c\u1ea5p, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. V\u1edbi ch\u1eef <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 12.96px; color: #ed1c24;\">&#8220;T\u00edn<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">&#8220;<\/span> \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00ean R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecb Th\u1ee7y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2403 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-9-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"453\" height=\"604\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-9-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-9-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-9-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-9-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-9.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 453px) 100vw, 453px\" title=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size: 14.4px;\"><em><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sang tr\u1ecdng cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><strong>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<br \/>\n<\/strong>V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t v\u1ea3i V\u00e2n n\u1ed5i xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n,<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #0000ff;\"> <a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-han-quoc\/\">r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/a><\/span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c R\u00e8m ph\u00fa th\u00e0nh nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ch\u00ednh ng\u1ea1ch, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c d\u00f5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4ng m\u00e0u Ghi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1eafng l\u00e0m c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng th\u00eam s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2405 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-11-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"422\" height=\"563\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-11-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-11-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-11-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-11-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-11.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 422px) 100vw, 422px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cao c\u1ea5p cho bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1<\/em>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><strong>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp<br \/>\n<\/strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp<\/span> <\/a><\/span>\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p mang l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt cho nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian. R\u00e8m c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb hai l\u1edbp r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c nhau: l\u1edbp voan m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 b\u00ean trong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng, hoa v\u0103n th\u00eau n\u1ed5i, h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft trag tr\u00ed, c\u00f2n l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">&#8211; Ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng, c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t: Do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m hai l\u1edbp n\u00ean lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp. Khi k\u00e9o l\u1edbp r\u00e8m b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y khung c\u1ea3nh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ch\u00f3i m\u1eaft b\u1edfi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00ec c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp voan m\u1ecfng b\u00ean trong ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">&#8211; C\u00e1ch \u00e2m t\u1ed1t:<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\"> <a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp<\/a><\/span><\/span> c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e1ch \u00e2m t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i cao su Silicon, r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i nhung, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng gian y\u00ean t\u0129nh trong ph\u00f2ng. N\u00ean th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, r\u00e8m c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7,&#8230;\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">&#8211; T\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng gian sang tr\u1ecdng, thanh l\u1ecbch, l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp, \u1edf trong l\u00e0 l\u1edbp r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i voan tr\u1eafng, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n, thanh l\u1ecbch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-phong-ngu\/\"> ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/a><\/span>.<\/span> \u0110\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m r\u00e8m c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng mang h\u01b0\u1edbng h\u01a1i c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n.\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp<\/a><\/span> <\/span>\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u trong nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> <span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-biet-thu\/\">bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1<\/a><\/span><\/span>, nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 cao c\u1ea5p hay nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. B\u1ed9 r\u00e8m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c con m\u1eaft th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb gia ch\u1ee7.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2408 aligncenter\" style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.4px;\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-14-300x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"448\" height=\"597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-14-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-14-510x680.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-14-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-14-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-29-14.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, l\u00e3n m\u1ea1n<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 thi c\u00f4ng, l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i, r\u00e8m c\u1eeda gia \u0111\u00ecnh, r\u00e8m v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t<br \/>\n<\/strong>Hi\u1ec7n nay, nhu c\u1ea7u l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m c\u1eeda kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u0103ng cao. khi m\u00e0 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0 v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng che n\u1eafng m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, khi ch\u1ecdn mua c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m c\u1eeda lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan t\u00e2m. b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\">R\u00e8m ph\u00fa th\u00e0nh<\/a><\/span> <\/span>t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 thi c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">L\u00fd do kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng ty R\u00e8m ph\u00fa th\u00e0nh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i:<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">1. T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, uy t\u00edn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\u00a0<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">2. Lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe v\u00e0 th\u1ea5u hi\